# TXTNodalExporter translations 2 ux uy
# TXTNodalExporter pressure 1 pressure
## export data in every nodes
# TXTNodalExporter translations 2 ux uy
# TXTNodalExporter pressure 1 pressure
## export data in gaus points
# TXTGaussPointExporter damage 7 x y normal_x normal_y damage slip slipPi
# TXTGaussPointExporter damage 7 x y normal_x normal_y damage strainT stralPLT
## displacement gauge uy x1coord y1coord x2coord y2coord 
DisplacementGauge LD displY uy 0e0 0.5e0 1e0 0.5e0
DisplacementGauge LD displX ux 0e0 0.5e0 1e0 0.5e0
## ForceGauge file_name gauge_name which_force how_many node_ids
ForceGauge LD react fx 18 0
ForceGauge LD load fx 18 18
## export VTK file
VTKElementExporter elems saveEvery 1e-1 cellData 1 damageT
VTKRCExporter rbc saveEvery 1e-1 cellData 1 damageT
